goal.ch:
學生修習完畢本課程應能具備:
1. 課堂教學實踐之能力;
2. 教學分析與評量之基本能力;
3. 教材評估與編撰之基本能力.

goal.en:
After this semester, students should have the basic abilities of:
1. teaching in a CSL class;
2. working on need and assessment;
3. developing CSL materials

outline.ch:
本課程授課重點在於:
1. 華語文教學實務相關文獻研討;
2. 華語文教學方法與策略之研討;
3. 華語文課堂教學分析與演練.

outline.en:
The contents of this course will focus on:
1. literatures review of CSL practice;
2. TCSL methods and strategies;
3. analyzing the instruction in a class;
4. teaching demonstration.
